At the moment, I see breakages in tensorflow-master-* builds in python3 and mac here:
https://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Tensorflow%20Jenkins%20Monitored%20builds/
But I do not see any long time trends. We will still look into what is going on, and see if there are any infrastructure issues we can address.

body:
At the moment, I see breakages in `tensorflow-master-*` builds in python3 and mac here:
https://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Tensorflow%20Jenkins%20Monitored%20builds/
But I do not see any long time trends. We will still look into what is going on, and see if there are any infrastructure issues we can address.
